<div class="fragment">
    <div class="header">
        <h3 class="title">Important Disclaimer</h3>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <!-- Standard Financial Services Disclaimer -->
        <div style="margin-bottom: 12px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E0E0E0;">
            <p><strong>Confidentiality & Intended Recipients</strong></p>
            <p>This material has been prepared by {{ company_name }}{% if recipient_type %} for {{ recipient_type }}{% endif %}. It is intended solely for the use of the addressee and may not be reproduced, distributed, or transmitted to any other person without our prior written consent.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 12px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E0E0E0;">
            <p><strong>Not Investment Advice</strong></p>
            <p>The information, opinions, and analyses presented herein do not constitute investment advice, a recommendation, or an offer to buy or sell any security. Past performance is not indicative of future results. Investments are subject to market risks, including possible loss of principal.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 12px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E0E0E0;">
            <p><strong>No Warranty</strong></p>
            <p>This material is provided on an "as-is" basis without warranties of any kind. {{ company_name }} makes no representations regarding the accuracy, completeness, or suitability of this information. Opinions and information are subject to change without notice.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 12px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E0E0E0;">
            <p><strong>Conflicts of Interest</strong></p>
            <p>{{ company_name }} and its affiliates may have financial interests in the securities or instruments discussed herein. Employees may hold positions in companies mentioned in this material.</p>
        </div>

        {% if include_ai_notice %}
        <div style="margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 12px; border-radius: 3px; border-left: 3px solid #1f77b4; background-color: #F0F7FF;">
            <p><strong>AI-Assisted Content</strong></p>
            <p>This material may have been produced with assistance from artificial intelligence tools. While AI assistance can enhance research efficiency, all conclusions and recommendations remain the professional responsibility of {{ company_name }}. Human review and judgment have been applied throughout the analysis.</p>
        </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div style="margin-bottom: 12px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E0E0E0;">
            <p><strong>Limitation of Liability</strong></p>
            <p>In no event shall {{ company_name }} be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from the use of this material. The user assumes all risks associated with the use of this information.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 12px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E0E0E0;">
            <p><strong>Regulatory Compliance</strong></p>
            <p>This material is issued in compliance with applicable laws and regulations in the {% if jurisdiction %}{{ jurisdiction }}{% else %}relevant jurisdiction{% endif %}. Recipients are responsible for complying with all applicable laws and regulations in their respective jurisdictions.</p>
        </div>

        {% if contact_email %}
        <div style="margin-top: 12px;">
            <p>For inquiries or to report concerns, please contact: <a href="mailto:{{ contact_email }}">{{ contact_email }}</a></p>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 12px; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid #E0E0E0; font-size: 0.85em; color: #7f7f7f;">
        <p style="margin: 0;">Prepared: {{ 'now'|date }}</p>
    </div>
</div>
